      "line": 37,
      "message": "We don't need to set the Loopback url (and should not).  Reason: the frontend artifacts (html,css,js) are being served from the Loopback server; i.e. the static files are being served from same IP and port as the Loopback server. As a result of not specifying the url, the static files will send request automatically to same IP and port.",
